headline.main: Katharine Cornell Is Dead at 81; Katharine Cornell Dies on Martha's Vineyard at 81 Formed Producing Unit The Audience Waited Born in Berlin Diminished Dazzle

snippet: Katharine Cornell, one of the great actresses of the American theater, died of pneumonia early yesterday at her home in Vineyard Haven, Mass., on Martha's Vineyard. She was 81 years old.
